'''Patameene District''' was an area on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Barlok/Legends|Barlok]]. It was one of the largest sections on the planet's [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]], straddling both rich and poor sections.<ref name="Outbound Flight">[[Outbound Flight (novel)|''Outbound Flight'']]</ref>

